Wednesday, July 5, 1995

MERIT DOCKET

95-544. Logsdon v. Fifth Third Bank of Toledo. Lucas County, No. L-93-225.

On review of order certifying a conflict. The court determines that no conflict exists within the meaning of S.Ct.Prac.R. IV(2)(B) and Whitelock v. Gilbane Bldg. Co. (1993), 66 Ohio St.3d 594, 613 N.E.2d 1032. This cause is therefore dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Dougla^ Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer and Cook, JJ., concur.
